<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>The Music minor teaches you to explore and understand the history, theory, and performance of music. Your professors and lecturers are active researchers and performing musicians who regularly have works performed, published, and recorded around the globe. You work closely with prominent artists-in-residence.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
